# Trendy Recipes Server

This is the REST API of the Trendy Recipes project.

## Prerequisites

Before running the project, make sure you have the following installed:

- Node.js
- Docker

## Development Setup

1. Run the following command to set up the development database (run migrations and seeds):

```shell
db:setup:dev
```

2. Start the development server by running:

```shell
npm run dev
```

This will start the server on http://127.0.0.1:3000.

## Running Tests

To run the tests, use the following command:

```shell
npm run test
```
